enge in creating code is the tons of problems that one will face over a lifetime of even a single project.</p>","excerpt":"Computer coding is like trying to hold a sword infront of a hydra. The moment you cut one of the heads, two new heads grow!   I wish I haveâ€¦","fields":{"tagSlugs":["/tags/blog/","/tags/creating-art/","/tags/talking-tech/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"Coding Complexity - Retaking ZTM (part 2)","tags":["blog","creating-art","talking-tech"],"date":"January 27, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/computer-coding-complexity-ZTM-part-2/"}}